  Maniac installation instructions

These are the installation guidelines for maniac.


REQUIREMENTS

 The only dependency on which Maniac relies is the Python interpreted.
 It is installed by default on most of (GNU)Linux distributions.


HOW TO PROCEED

 Well, it's pretty simple, you only have to copy the main script into
 a bin directory:

 $ cp maniac.py ~/.local/bin/maniac
 $ sudo cp maniac.py /usr/bin/maniac

 Or anything like that should do.
